Laith Nakli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laith_Nakli 0 Laith Nakli (born December 1, 1969) is an English born actor and producer best known for his role in the 2017 movie The Wall as the voice of the mythical sniper named Juba, the 2017 miniseries The Long Road Home and 2018 movie 12 Strong as Commander Ahmed Lal.
